    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a collector-grade find that looks and drives as if it were brand new. The exterior paint is flawless, displaying a deep, showroom-quality luster without a single scratch, chip, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin is immaculate, with the leather and trim showing no signs of wear and still retaining that new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history and zero issues. Every feature and electronic component functions exactly as intended, providing a driving experience that is smooth, quiet, and powerful. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in such pristine, factory-fresh condition.",
