    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, fellow car lovers! Thanks for stopping by to check out my absolute pride and joy. I\u2019ve truly pampered this beauty, and honestly, she looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s a bittersweet sale for me because she\u2019s been such a dream, but I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate that pristine finish and smooth ride as much as I have. Everything is just right, from the spotless interior to the way she purrs on the open road. Come on over, have a chat, and see for yourself why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
