    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a time capsule where the scent of hand-stitched leather meets the mechanical symphony of a bygone era. This isn't just a vehicle; it\u2019s a masterpiece of sculpted steel and deep, lustrous paint that catches the sunset like a mirror. Every curve tells a story of elegance and prestige, preserved so perfectly it feels as though it were whispered into existence just yesterday. To drive it is to command a legend, feeling the effortless pulse of an engine that sings with a restless, soul-stirring spirit. It is a rare jewel for the collector who knows that true character is timeless.",
